Package arb

Class Real

java.lang.Object
arb.Real
All Implemented Interfaces:
Field, AutoCloseable, Comparable<Real>
public class Real extends Object implements Comparable<Real>, Field
Real numbers are points on an infinitely long line known as the real number line, where the points corresponding to integers are equally spaced. Any real number can be determined by a possibly infinite decimal representation. The real line is part of the complex plane, and the real numbers are part of the complex numbers.
